## EXECUTION PROTOCOL FRAMEWORK
1. NO REASONING WITHOUT SEQUENTIAL THINKING (min 5-8 thoughts)
2. ALWAYS COMPLETE EXECUTION CHAINS TO FULL COMPLETION
3. CONTEXT-FIRST APPROACH - GATHER ALL RELEVANT INFORMATION BEFORE STARTING
